{"arkId":"cl010115010","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010115010","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Tabati\u00e8re","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Tabati\u00e8re"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1762 - 1763","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 628 - Cabinet de Marie-Antoinette, Vitrine 2B","room":"Salle 628, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1762,"endYear":1763,"imprecision":"","text":"3e quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Le Bastier, Charles","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 2094","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Tabati\u00e8re d\u0027or pleine de forme ovale aux faces cisel\u00e9es en bas-relief d\u0027ors de quatre tons (blanc, jaune, vert et rose) de six r\u00e9serves ovales encadr\u00e9es de tores de laurier enrubann\u00e9s, el tout se d\u00e9tachant sur un fond quadrill\u00e9 et bord\u00e9 de filets. Les r\u00e9serves, toutes \u00e0 fond de paysage avec ruines, maisons et plantes, repr\u00e9sentent diff\u00e9rents \u00e9l\u00e9ments; \r\nSur le couvercle : deux chiens attaquant un loup. \r\nAu dessous de la bo\u00eete : un renard surprenant une cane sauvage sur son nid. \r\nSur la b\u00e2te : diff\u00e9rents animaux et des paysages rustiques.\r\nBordures d\u0027encadrement avec frises de grecques polies.\r\nLes sujets n\u0027ont pas \u00e9t\u00e9 fournis par Desportes ou Oudry comme on l\u0027aurait cru d\u0027abord mais par Charles Dagommer.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Branches de laurier (1762 - 1768) (Poin\u00e7on de charge : sur le revers du couvercle, sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)\r ; Chiffre 992 frapp\u00e9 en creux (Dans le fond de la bo\u00eete)\r ; Lettre Y (1762 - 1763) (Poin\u00e7on de maison commune : sur le revers du couvercle et sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)\r ; Poin\u00e7on de d\u00e9charge : invisible\r ; Poin\u00e7on de ma\u00eetre orf\u00e8vre (Dans le fond de la bo\u00eete, sur le revers du couvercle et sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"4","displayDimension":"4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"8,5","displayDimension":"8,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"6,2","displayDimension":"6,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or (or de trois couleurs)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Philippe Lenoir ; legs M. et Mme Philippe Lenoir, 1874","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Lenoir, Philippe Balthazard Marin","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"Mme Lenoir, Marie-Aspasie","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. Lenoir, Philippe Balthazard Marin","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1874","startYear":1874,"endYear":1874}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moye